</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="Comprehensive Hair Treatments &amp; Solutions">
  <h4 class="pg-h">Expert Hair Revitalization Services</h4>
  <p class="pg-text">At Menon MediSpa, we blend clinical expertise with luxury to deliver transformative hair restoration and scalp treatments. Our advanced HydraFacial Keravive and PRP therapies address hair thinning and scalp health concerns using proven technologies.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Our medical-grade hair services address specific scalp concerns using innovative technologies and pharmaceutical-grade products. Led by expert medical professionals, each treatment is tailored to your unique hair and scalp profile.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">From revitalizing scalp health to stimulating new hair growth, our cutting-edge treatments provide visible, long-lasting results. Experience the difference of clinically-effective hair restoration in our serene Millburn, NJ medical spa.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Comprehensive Hair Treatments &amp; Solutions</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">Experience our specialized range of advanced hair restoration treatments, expertly designed to revitalize your scalp and enhance hair growth. Click To See More!</p>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/02127013d183.jpg" alt="HydraFacialKeravive_Treatment_5_edited.jpg" width="290" height="290" loading="lazy" />
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/hydrafacial-keravive">HYDRAFACIAL KERAVIVE</a>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/e6d509254f0c.jpg" alt="Model with Curly Hair" width="402" height="673" loading="lazy" />
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/platelet-rich-plasma-hair-millburn">PRP HAIR RESTORATION</a>
</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="What Our Clients Say">
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/30cfb9e87c60.png" alt="Untitled-4.png" width="1440" height="626" loading="lazy" />
  <h3 class="pg-h">What Our Clients Say</h3>
  <blockquote class="pg-quote">Jennifer is amazing. Her aura and energy makes you feel welcomed and comfortable. Love our sessions! And my girl Rose Marie, the receptionist, is just lovely! I always leave with great joy after seeing them.</blockquote>
  <p class="pg-text">Alexa C.</p>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/5be44787b3a9.png" alt="Social Proof (5 Star Google Reviews)" width="143" height="74" loading="lazy" />
</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="Why Choose Menon MediSpa for Your Hair Restoration Needs?">
  <h2 class="pg-h">Why Choose Menon MediSpa for Your Hair Restoration Needs?</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Our comprehensive approach integrates advanced scalp care with medical-grade procedures to deliver truly transformative results. We create customized treatment plans that address both immediate concerns and long-term hair wellness goals.</p>
  <h4 class="pg-h">Our Integrated Treatment Philosophy</h4>
  <p class="pg-text">At Menon MediSpa, we understand that optimal hair restoration often requires a multi-faceted approach. Our specialists are trained in both scalp health and advanced procedures like HydraFacial Keravive and PRP hair therapy, allowing us to create personalized solutions that enhance your natural hair growth potential.</p>
  <h4 class="pg-h">What to Expect</h4>
  <p class="pg-text">Your experience begins with a thorough consultation to understand your hair concerns and goals. Whether you're receiving a HydraFacial Keravive treatment or PRP hair restoration therapy, you'll enjoy attentive care in our relaxing, clinical environment. We use only premium products and advanced techniques to ensure safe, effective results.</p>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/b6de27df4c69.png" alt="image.png" width="315" height="313" loading="lazy" />
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/bcdc3a29fdee.png" alt="image.png" width="315" height="313" loading="lazy" />
</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="Frequently asked questions">
  <h2 class="pg-h">Frequently asked questions</h2>
  <p class="pg-btnlabel">Which hair treatment is right for me?</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Which hair treatment is right for me?</h3>
