  <h3 class="pg-h">How many sessions will I need?</h3>
  <p class="pg-btnlabel">How soon will I see results?</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">How soon will I see results?</h3>
  <p class="pg-btnlabel">Are the treatments painful?</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Are the treatments painful?</h3>
</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="Begin Your Transformation Today">
  <h2 class="pg-h">Begin Your Transformation Today</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Menon Medispa Millburn NJ</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Ready to experience the benefits of Hair Restoration with Dr. Aditi Menon? Take the first step toward Luxurious Hair by scheduling your personal consultation at Menon Medispa in Millburn, NJ.</p>
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/consultation">Schedule Consultation</a>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/b1a819f35921.webp" alt="Menon Office Staff.webp" width="431" height="560" loading="lazy" />
</section>
